{"tid":2108034,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"高力國際料今年全年整體一線街舖租金按年跌33%","createTime":"2020-07-14T09:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T09:21:27.000Z","uid":166360,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"95d79b3b475a11f554845dbfb8ee1277ecc3d831","tid":2108034,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:08:53.000Z","msg":"高力國際料今年全年整體一線街舖租金按年跌33%<br />\n2020-07-14 HKT 15:37<br />\n<br />\n&quot;國際物業顧問高力國際發表報告指，新型肺炎疫情打擊本港零售業，拖累上季整體一線街舖租金按季跌9.3%，當中中環跌14%，旺角、尖沙咀及銅鑼灣跌逾7%至逾8%。該行預計，今年全年整體一線街舖租金將會按年跌33%。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537655-20200714.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537655-20200714.htm&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuG5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=a32440bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537655-20200714.htm&h=7af20579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537655-20200714.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4eb5b4c46f24391b0f7d74cd22281d220e435a59","tid":2108034,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:21:27.000Z","msg":"樓價照升三成<br />\n繼續大牛市<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}